                                Label{//图标说明
                                    anchors.top: icon_1.bottom
                                    anchors.topMargin: 1
                                    anchors.horizontalCenter: parent.horizontalCenter		//Label居中靠齐parent
                                    horizontalAlignment:Text.AlignHCenter			//Label中的文字居中显示
                                    font.pixelSize: 11
                                    font.family: myMDCCommand.Language?"微软雅黑":"Arial"
                                    color:"#697d8e"
                                    text:name
                                    elide: Text.ElideRight					//右省略
                                    width: 33
                                }‘


PS：如果不指定horizontalAlignment:Text.AlignHCenter，将导致文字左靠齐parent
